# Express ToDo App [![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/sarpisik/express-todo-app.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/sarpisik/express-todo-app) [![Coverage Status](https://coveralls.io/repos/github/sarpisik/express-todo-app/badge.svg?branch=master)](https://coveralls.io/github/sarpisik/express-todo-app?branch=master) [![Maintainability](https://api.codeclimate.com/v1/badges/37e590bb4c706ee3e9fd/maintainability)](https://codeclimate.com/github/sarpisik/express-todo-app/maintainability) [![code style: prettier](https://img.shields.io/badge/code_style-prettier-ff69b4.svg?style=flat-square)](https://github.com/prettier/prettier) Node js based a MVC web application.   Demo
  Code
## **Features** ### **Model** > Object Data Modeling (ODM) by [Mongoose](https://mongoosejs.com/). ### **View** > [Pug](https://pugjs.org/api/getting-started.html) template engine. ### **Controller** > [Express js](https://expressjs.com/).
